OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773349567
OL,3,C97-year-old woman 'not happy' over
OL,4,Cplans to demolish flats
OL,6,FA 97-year-old woman from Hollingdean
OL,7,Fhas said she is 'not happy' about
OL,8,Fplans to demolish her flat.
OL,10,FRita King's home, which she's lived in
OL,11,Ffor 35 years, is one of 554 flats in 8
OL,12,Fblocks in Brighton and Hove which no
OL,13,Flonger meet safety standards and are
OL,14,Fearmarked to be knocked down.
OL,16,FOver 1000 residents would be impacted
OL,17,Fby the decision.
OL,19,FTwo of the blocks are in Hollingdean,
OL,20,Fwith five in north Whitehawk and one
OL,21,Fin Kemptown.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773349567
OL,3,C97-year-old woman 'not happy' over
OL,4,Cplans to demolish flats
OL,6,FBrighton and Hove City Council will
OL,7,Fmake a final decision on Thursday 19
OL,8,FMarch after structural surveys found
OL,9,Fthey would not withstand a collapse -
OL,10,Fin the case of an explosion or large
OL,11,Ffire.
OL,13,FThe council are aiming to demolish the
OL,14,Fflats over a period of three to five
OL,15,Fyears and would replace them with
OL,16,Fnewer homes.
OL,18,FMs King said: "I'm not happy
OL,19,Fobviously, I've lived here for 35
OL,20,Fyears, I love it .... everything's
OL,21,Fperfect for me in my eyes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773349567
OL,3,C97-year-old woman 'not happy' over
OL,4,Cplans to demolish flats
OL,6,F"But things change, and you have to
OL,7,Faccept change.
OL,9,F"Do any of us know what's going to
OL,10,Fhappen? When is it going to happen?
OL,12,F"I could have left in my box a long
OL,13,Ftime before that happens.
OL,15,F"Where are they going to put us all?
OL,16,FDoes anybody know?"
OL,18,FFellow resident Phil Jeffries said:
OL,19,F"(I'm) broken hearted, they're
OL,20,Ffabulous flats.
OL,26,@{D@Bpm{D@Fpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773349567
OL,3,C97-year-old woman 'not happy' over
OL,4,Cplans to demolish flats
OL,6,F"They've got 8 blocks to pull down,
OL,7,F460 families to rehouse, they've got
OL,8,Ffive years to do all this.
OL,10,FHow are they going to build all these
OL,11,Fproperties in five years? It's not
OL,12,Frealistic."
OL,14,FITV Meridian has been told older
OL,15,Ftenants like Rita will be found
OL,16,Fsuitable sheltered housing, while
OL,17,Fyounger residents could be offered
OL,18,Fgrants of up to 50 thousand pounds to
OL,19,Fbuy privately.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773349567
OL,3,C97-year-old woman 'not happy' over
OL,4,Cplans to demolish flats
OL,6,FCllr Gill Williams (Lab) from Brighton
OL,7,Fand Hove City Council said: "We're
OL,8,Fproposing now to initiate a demolition
OL,9,Fnotice, however, we don't want to be
OL,10,Ffrightening people.
OL,12,F"The demolition notice lasts for seven
OL,13,Fyears and we're anticipating this
OL,14,Fwhole programme of demolition is going
OL,15,Fto take 3 to 5 years.
OL,17,F"The panels that the blocks are
OL,18,Factually built with in the 60s are now
OL,19,Fdeemed to be not as safe as we'd like
OL,20,Fthem to be.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773349567
OL,3,C97-year-old woman 'not happy' over
OL,4,Cplans to demolish flats
OL,6,F"So we could spend millions on
OL,7,Frefurbishing but we're going to end up
OL,8,Fhaving to do this at some point anyway.
OL,10,F"So yes we anticipate we'll be able to
OL,11,Frehouse them but it is over time, and
OL,12,Fwhat happen, once we demolish we will
OL,13,Fbe rebuilding.
OL,15,F"So long term we hope to then have
OL,16,Fmore social housing in the city, not
OL,17,Fless."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
